</taxonomicName>
(
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">E. Martinez &amp; A. Ibarra</emphasis>
40654 (MEXU); 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A. Carter</emphasis>
4985, 5195 (MEXU) with short corolla but erect sepals.
</paragraph>
